      "raw_text": "County Superintendent of Schools\nr. G. Mcfarland stated last night\nthat all of the papers of the pupils\nwho took the eighth grade examina-\ntions Thursday and Friday at the\nMasonic temple will be graded by\nJanuary 20.\n\n\nExaminations were held at 3S\nplaces in Spokane county and Mr..\nMcfarland is of the opinion that\n900 students took the tests."
